6: Alk! I'm glad you could make it.
9:
Congratulations on the promotion to 
chief supervisor, Rico!
11:
I'm glad the succession is finally settled. 
Here, darling, a little gift to celebrate.
14:
Oh, you didn't have to!
Thank you for coming, everyone.
18:
Man, when I saw how big the mansion is, 
I was honestly a bit worried I had the 
wrong address...
21:
We're in charge of Palpebra's main 
water supply, after all. 
Utilities are a pretty stable business.
22:
I can't believe I'M the one inheriting it. 
This is all thanks to your help, Alk!
26:
You're the one who did all the work. 
Congrats, Rico!
31:
I-I wouldn't been able to solve the trial 
without you, though! 
Really, I can't thank you enough!
36: Lady Rico, might I have this dance?
41:
Uh, um... Sorry, I, I already said I'd dance 
with someone else!
49:
Huh? Oh, r-right. Rico—
I mean LADY Rico has already promised 
me the first dance of the evening!
59:
Oh, did you hear that? 
Lady Rico wishes to dance!
60:
Oh, my, how lovely! 
Shoo, shoo, clear the dancefloor!
64:
Wait, wait I can't—! 
Rico! Rico, what should we do?!
68:
Alk, I'm so sorry...
I just wanted an excuse NOT to dance, 
but looks like we don't have much 
choice.
71:
(Psst, Rico. I-I've never danced in my 
life! What do I do?!)
74:
(Just follow my lead. Whatever I do, 
copy it!)
84:
Splendid! Stunning! Lady Rico's 
footwork is stellar!
85:
What an adorable pair! 
They're perfectly in sync with each 
other!
88:
You're doing great, Alk.
Left foot, right foot, left, right, left, left—
100:
I saw your dance, Rico. Absolutely 
marvelous!
103:
Father! But—
Are you sure it's all right for you to be up 
and walking? You should be in bed!
106:
It's my little girl's big day! 
We're all so proud of you, sweetums. 
At least let me say hello to the 
gentleman with you.
111:
Alk, yes? I heard all about you. 
With Rico being how she is, I was afraid 
I'd never see this day! 
You have my deepest thanks.
115:
Oh, gosh, I really didn't do much. 
I just helped a little on the way.
117:
My! What a humble, young man! 
Yes, I can tell you'll take excellent care of 
my little Rico. Have you picked a date 
for the wedding?
